textBeforeTable: Base Game General BooksEdit In The Sims 3: Into the Future, the books in Oasis Landing are E-Books. There are a wide range of premade books that cannot be bought, but are instead gained through opportunities in work or adventures. Sims can buy many premade books from the bookstore, a rabbit hole found in premade neighborhoods such as Riverview. General books also appear to read in the library.
